# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/).

## [1.3.0] - 2025-09-26

### Added

- Add validator on P-chain.
- Method setAfterTxConfirmationCallback.

### Changed

- Fee percentage changed to delegation fee (a percentage in base points) in type Stake.
- Methods for fetching stake information.


## [1.2.1] - 2025-08-19

### Changed

- Fixed typo for IMPORT_P transaction type.


## [1.2.0] - 2025-08-07

### Added

- Native P-chain transfer.
- Reward claiming for rNat projects.
- Voting on Flare foundation proposals.
- Support for smart accounts.
- Public key recovery from a submitted transaction in EIP-1193 based wallets.

### Changed

- P-chain transaction updates.


## [1.1.0] - 2025-05-23

### Added

- Reward claiming.
- Support for common wallets.


## [1.0.0] - 2025-02-19

### Added

- Initial version.